import org.apache.nifi.processor.io.StreamCallback
import groovy.json.JsonSlurper
import groovy.json.JsonOutput
import java.nio.charset.StandardCharsets
import java.time.Instant
import java.time.ZoneOffset
import java.time.format.DateTimeFormatter

def flowFile = session.get()
if(!flowFile) return

// Read dynamic start/end time attributes (epoch values from NiFi)
def startTimeAttr = flowFile.getAttribute("starttime")
def endTimeAttr   = flowFile.getAttribute("endtime")

def formatter = DateTimeFormatter.ofPattern("yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm:ss").withZone(ZoneOffset.UTC)
def startTimeStr = startTimeAttr ? formatter.format(Instant.ofEpochMilli(startTimeAttr.toLong())) : null
def endTimeStr   = endTimeAttr ? formatter.format(Instant.ofEpochMilli(endTimeAttr.toLong())) : null

flowFile = session.write(flowFile, { inputStream, outputStream ->

    def jsonText = inputStream.getText('UTF-8')
    def data = new JsonSlurper().parseText(jsonText)

    def transformed = []
    def now = Instant.now()

    data.each { record ->
        def timestampMs = record.timestamp
        def eventTime = formatter.format(Instant.ofEpochMilli(timestampMs))

        record.stats.each { stat ->
            transformed << [
                start_time                : startTimeStr,
                end_time                  : endTimeStr,
                timestamp_ms              : timestampMs,
                event_time                : eventTime,
                queue_id                  : stat.queueId,
                site_id                   : stat.siteId,
                zone_id                   : stat.zoneId,
                count                     : stat.count ?: 0,
                wait_time                 : stat.waitTime ?: 0,
                active_servers            : stat.activeServers ?: 0,
                active_gates              : stat.activeGates ?: 0,
                avg_server_service_time   : stat.avgServerServiceTime ?: 0,
                avg_gate_service_time     : stat.avgGateServiceTime ?: 0,
                entry_count               : stat.entry ?: 0,
                exit_count                : stat.exit ?: 0,
                created_at                : formatter.format(now)
            ]
        }
    }

    outputStream.write(JsonOutput.prettyPrint(JsonOutput.toJson(transformed)).getBytes(StandardCharsets.UTF_8))

} as StreamCallback)

session.transfer(flowFile, REL_SUCCESS)
